class CefSchemeHandlerFactory
extends CefBase

Class that creates CefSchemeHandler instances. The methods of this class will always be called on the IO thread.

Method Detail

Create

public virtual CefRefPtr< CefSchemeHandler > Create( CefRefPtr< CefBrowser > browser, const CefString& scheme_name, CefRefPtr< CefRequest > request )= 0;
Return a new scheme handler instance to handle the request. |browser| will be the browser window that initiated the request. If the request was initiated using the CefWebURLRequest API |browser| will be NULL. The |request| object passed to this method will not contain cookie data.
